me":"a","properties":{"href":"http://avogadrocorp.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Avogadro Corp (William Hertling)"}]},{"type":"text","value":": This novel pitches a precise and believable scenario of how an AI could run out of control. It's a startling difference from your typical Terminator narrative, and deeply unsettling."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/23463279-designing-data-intensive-applications"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Designing Data-Intensive Applications (Martin Kleppmann)"}]},{"type":"text","value":": A high-level tour of tools and approaches for system design."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.tor.com/2010/08/05/divided-by-infinity/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Divided by Infinity (Robert Wilson)"}]},{"type":"text","value":": A short story that may briefly make you question your own reality."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Permutation_City"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Permutation City (Greg Egan)"}]},{"type":"text","value":": This book helped me grapple with the meaning of life under nihilism and explores some fascinating aspects of transhumanism."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/23692271-sapiens"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sapiens (Yuval Harari)"}]},{"type":"text","value":": A history of humankind, from the agricultural revolution to the current day."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"child